{"tid":387074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全城中伏]中環海濱摩天輪用地可以唔起摩天輪都得，用o黎擺酒都得","createTime":"2017-09-04T11:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T11:46:32.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0dbfb7098818df5c3389b2fe7e5df9052d181f73","tid":387074,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:12:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201709/03/P2017090300367.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201709%2F03%2FP2017090300367.htm&d=PomoZKOrOteIh%2Fx5rwoiWgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7da3cd0b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201709/03/P2017090300367.htm</a><br />\n<strong><br />\n待用地轉交新營辦商之後，新的三年短期租約會隨即開始。若新營辦商需安裝新摩天輪，其開始營運摩天輪的時間，將視乎新營辦商取得相關許可和牌照的時間。在進行所需工程和申請牌照期間，新營辦商亦可以在用地內提供輔助設施或舉辦活動，讓公眾盡早享用用地內的設施。 <br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老味，瑞士佬呢次交硬學費"},{"pid":"6212d603bc7129a48a08b73e8c9f7ba25b250d80","tid":387074,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:18:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201709/03/P2017090300367.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201709%2F03%2FP2017090300367.htm&d=PomoZKOrOteIh%2Fx5rwoiWgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7da3cd0b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201709/03/P2017090300367.htm</a><br />\n<strong><br />\n待用地轉交新營辦商之後，新的三年短期租約會隨即開始。若新營辦商需安裝新摩天輪，其開始營運摩天輪的時間，將視乎新營辦商取得相關許可和牌照的時間。在進行所需工程和申請牌照期間，新營辦商亦可以在用地內提供輔助設施或舉辦活動，讓公眾盡早享用用地內的設施。 <br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老味，瑞士佬呢次交硬學費</blockquote><br />\n屌 咁撚仆街 有冇人起到tecl 背後金主係邊個"},{"pid":"9dd0d04501455ac7980671ab96998963e86cf827","tid":387074,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:42:37.000Z","msg":"唔撚怪得下一手根本唔介意你賣唔賣摩天輪，有又得，無又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6216e6a